# Secrets — never commit. Signing keys, App Store Connect API keys, and
# Firebase configs must be supplied to Codemagic via its own secure
# environment/integration settings, not via the repo.
# NOTE: excluding google-services.json means the android-apk Codemagic
# workflow in codemagic.yaml will fail (the Gradle plugin requires the file
# to exist) until it's supplied another way — see the summary for options.
google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
*.p8
*.p12
*.jks
*.keystore
key.properties
.env
.env.*
*.pem
